reviewText: When I ordered this, I didn't know what to really expect. Never imported anything before. I was happy that I did. The description was what they claimed it to be, and it was brand new. I will use this company again when I go for the remaining episodes for this particular show.

It is a great random series with the somewhat standard fair of all the girls liking the main guy, but he is kind of really dense, so never really goes anywhere.

I just wish I knew if this had English subs.  Had watched it on Crunchyroll.
